NGUVA YE UPOROFITA

0:00:05.580,0:00:09.620
Pane gakava pamusoro pe mwana.

0:00:09.620,0:00:14.320
Unofanira kuyananisa. Pano dikanwa ruyananiso.

0:00:14.320,0:00:17.300
Ichokwadi.

0:00:17.300,0:00:20.960
Dzimwe nguva, hatizivi kuti chinetso chedu chiri kubva kupi.

0:00:20.960,0:00:25.900
Tinotanga kukumbira Mwari kuti atiropafadze asi dzimwe nguva, kune makomo mune imwe nzvimbo

0:00:25.900,0:00:27.880
awo akamira kutipikisa.

0:00:27.880,0:00:31.720
Tinogona kutadza kuzviona se chinetso asi chinetso chikuru.

0:00:31.720,0:00:35.480
Kana chiratidzo ichi chisina kupihwa kwauri, ucharamba uchikumbira kuti uve nekubudirira.

0:00:35.480,0:00:38.880
Hakugoni kuve nekubudirira pasina yananiso.

0:00:38.880,0:00:41.140
Munhu wa Mwari, zvamataura pamusoro pezvangu ndezve chokwadi.

0:00:41.140,0:00:45.800
Pasina yananiso iyoyo, kuwana musikana uyu, kumira uchiuya kuzoti,

0:00:45.800,0:00:49.520
"Ndini baba", haugone kuzviwana zvakanaka muupenyu.

0:00:49.520,0:00:52.240
Munhu wa Mwari, ichokwadi.

0:00:52.240,0:00:55.380
Munhu wa Mwari, ndapota ndibatsirei. Ndinoda kutora mwana uyu kuti adzoke mu hupenyu hwangu.

0:00:55.380,0:00:58.760
Ndapota ndibatsirei, munhu wa Mwari.

0:00:58.760,0:01:01.880
Pane nguva iyo vakakutora kuenda kun'anga.

0:01:01.880,0:01:03.060
Unozviyeuka here?

0:01:03.060,0:01:04.040
Ichokwadi, Munhu wa Mwari.

0:01:04.040,0:01:05.840
Iwe wakanga uchitsvaka kununurwa.

0:01:05.840,0:01:08.300
Pane nguva iyo vakakupa hengechefu.

0:01:08.300,0:01:09.480
Ichokwadi.

0:01:09.480,0:01:10.380
Zvakanaka.

0:01:10.380,0:01:13.520
Mushure medzikinuro yako, uchawana mwana uyu zvakare.

0:01:13.520,0:01:17.680
Uye iwe ucharipa mukadzi uyu uchiti, "Ndine urombo". Uyu mukadzi achakuregerera.

0:01:17.680,0:01:24.320
Zvino, iwe unogona kutanga hupenyu hwako zvakare.

0:01:24.320,0:01:27.980
Ndinokutendai, Jesu.

0:01:27.980,0:01:33.280
NGUVA YE HUCHAPUPU

0:01:33.280,0:01:36.920
Mushure me huprofita ihwohwo ne kudzikinurwa kwe murume uyu

0:01:36.920,0:01:42.740
iye akadzokera kunyika yake, uko akakwanisa kuwana mukadzi wacho.

0:01:50.580,0:01:52.520
Kubvira pamakore gumi namana.

0:01:52.520,0:01:53.880
Rega ndikutaurire pamusoro pedzikinuro.

0:01:53.880,0:01:57.180
Kana vakataura newe - mumwe-pa-mumwe - ndiyo dzikinuro.

0:01:57.180,0:02:00.060
Mubvunzo nemhinduro ndizvo zvavanopa.

0:02:00.060,0:02:02.060
Zita rangu ndi Frank Dagbe.

0:02:02.060,0:02:04.260
Ini ndinobva ku Ghana.

0:02:04.260,0:02:10.660
Chokutanga, ndinoda kuvonga munhu wa Mwari zvikuru kwazvo nokuda kwe kuzvibvumira kushandiswa na Mwari Samasimba

0:02:10.660,0:02:14.560
ku fukunura midzi ye chikonzero che dambudziko rangu.

0:02:14.560,0:02:23.100
Ndakanga ndiri pano muna December 2008 ndichitsvaga budiriro, munhu wa Mwari akandiona.

0:02:23.100,0:02:27.760
Ndakanga ndagara pano iye akati ini ndaitsvaga kubudirira

0:02:27.760,0:02:30.480
asi pane gakava pamusoro pe mwana muhupenyu hwangu.

0:02:30.480,0:02:34.320
Ndinofanira kuenda ndino yananisa ne kunotenda mukadzi uyu zvakanyanyisa

0:02:34.320,0:02:37.240
kusati kwave nebudiriro muupenyu hwangu.

0:02:37.240,0:02:42.240
Chaizvoizvo, izvozvo zvakaitwa uye sezvandiri pano,

0:02:42.240,0:02:47.720
Ndinogona kutaura kuti kune budiriro izere muupenyu hwangu.

0:02:47.720,0:02:49.940
Ndisati ndasvika pari nhasi, zvinhu zvakanga zvisiri kufamba zvakanaka.

0:02:49.940,0:02:53.820
Ndicho chikonzero ndakauya pano nokuti ndakanga ndichiona Emmanuel TV

0:02:53.820,0:02:58.300
uye ndakaona izvo Mwari anoshandisa munhu wa Mwari kuti aite muupenyu hwevanhu.

0:02:58.300,0:03:00.620
Akauya pano nokuda kwe budiriro -

0:03:00.620,0:03:04.040
kwakanga kusina basa, kusina mari.

0:03:04.040,0:03:08.020
Ndakati, tarisa, iri ndiro dambudziko raunaro.

0:03:08.020,0:03:11.140
Ndipo pane midzi ye dambudziko rako.

0:03:11.140,0:03:17.220
Makore akapfuura, pakanga pane mukadzi wawakangosiya.

0:03:17.220,0:03:20.520
Iwe wakati hauzive; iwe uri mukomana muduku.

0:03:20.520,0:03:22.840
Iwe ndiwe muridzi wemwana.

0:03:22.840,0:03:28.720
Ndakati, usafunganya. Mushure me dzikinuro iyi, iwe uchaona zvinhu zvese

0:03:28.720,0:03:31.160
uye ivowo vachange vachikutsvaka.

0:03:31.160,0:03:33.900
Apo unenge uchivatsvaga, ivo vanenge vachikutsvaka.

0:03:33.900,0:03:39.700
Pavanokuona iye zvino ivo vachati, "Ndinokutendai, Jesu! Tange tichikutsvaka!"

0:03:44.860,0:03:48.860
Munhu wa Mwari akati pane kukakavara pamusoro pomwana.

0:03:48.860,0:03:52.960
Zvechokwadi, asati aberekwa, ndakamuramba,

0:03:52.960,0:03:55.880
ndichitaura kuti ini handini akaitisa mai vake pamuviri.

0:03:55.880,0:04:00.440
Vakauya kuzosangana nevabereki vangu ipapo baba vangu vakandidana kure nevabereki vake

0:04:00.440,0:04:04.640
kuti ndinofanira kuzvi gamuchira nokuti ivewo munhurume; vakapfuura nemune zvose

0:04:04.640,0:04:08.760
apo vaive kuchikoro, saka ini ndaifanira kutaura chokwadi asi ini ndakaramba.

0:04:08.760,0:04:12.840
Uchirirai baba vake.

0:04:12.840,0:04:15.440
Unoona baba vakanaka.

0:04:15.440,0:04:20.080
Baba vake vakanaka vakamudana pakavanzika ndokuti, "Tarisai, ini ndiri murume.

0:04:20.080,0:04:28.440
Zvandiri kuona zvino, kubva pakuonekwa kwe zvinhu, pamuviri pacho pakange pane mwedzi mitatu -

0:04:28.440,0:04:30.200
iwe ndiwe muridzi.

0:04:30.200,0:04:31.360
Akati, "Kwete kwete kwete!"

0:04:31.360,0:04:34.760
Izvo zvakataurwa nomunhu wa Mwari ndezve chokwadi

0:04:34.760,0:04:39.780
nokuti handina kumboziva kuti iri ndiro dambudziko racho.

0:04:39.780,0:04:47.620
Ndakarangana ne umwe munin'ina wangu kuti anditsigire pakuramba kwangu.

0:04:47.620,0:04:49.760
Kukudzwa ngakuve kuna Mwari!

0:04:49.760,0:04:52.520
Tarisa nzira iyo Mwari akandidana nayo muupenyu hwake.

0:04:52.520,0:04:56.340
Akabva ku Ghana achichema asi Ishe akati, "Kwete kwete!

0:04:56.340,0:05:01.660
Mwana uyo wemakore gumi nemana akapfuura wawakaramba!

0:05:01.660,0:05:06.400
Dzokera unotora mwana iyeye. Kana zvisina kudaro, iwe uchava murombo kupfuura izvi ".

0:05:06.400,0:05:08.860
Handina kumboziva kuti ndiro dambudziko racho.

0:05:08.860,0:05:11.780
Chaizvoizvo, ndakanga ndichitsvaga budiriro.

0:05:11.780,0:05:16.180
Ndinoda kuratidza kuvonga kwangu kumunhu wa Mwari nekuzvibvumira

0:05:16.180,0:05:20.540
kuti ashandiswe zvakanyanya nokuda kwedambudziko rangu.

0:05:20.540,0:05:25.900
Zvino, mushure mokuporofitwa, kwave ne budiriro mu hupenyu hwangu.

0:05:25.900,0:05:29.660
Ndine chibvumirano zvino. Kunyange zvandiri pano, pane foni yauya kwandiri.

0:05:29.660,0:05:32.320
Chibvumirano chakandimirira ku Ghana izvozvi.

0:05:32.320,0:05:35.860
Munhu wa Mwari, ndinokutendai zvikuru pane izvo Mwari akakushandisai imi kuti muite muupenyu hwangu.

0:05:35.860,0:05:44.680
Iwe uchangotanga nokuti ndiri kukuona iwe uchizofamba kuenda ku Canada.

0:05:44.680,0:05:46.020
Iwe unofanirwa kugadzirira.

0:05:46.020,0:05:47.660
Ngatibvunzei musikana muduku.

0:05:47.660,0:05:49.220
Iwe urikunzwa sei zvino,

0:05:49.220,0:05:52.520
zvino zvawawana baba vako mushure memakore gumi nemana?

0:05:52.520,0:05:54.840
Zita rangu ndi Hilda Dagbe.

0:05:54.840,0:05:56.840
Ndine makore 14.

0:05:56.880,0:06:00.080
Ndiri kufara kuona baba vangu zvino.

0:06:04.500,0:06:08.360
Dai risiri shoko iri, murume uyu angadai aramba achizviramba nokusingaperi.

0:06:08.360,0:06:15.940
Musikana wechidiki ati ini ndiri kufara iye zvino. Mushure memakore gumi nemana, ndava kukwanisa kuziva baba vangu.

0:06:15.940,0:06:18.260
Munhu wa Mwari, ndinokutendai.

0:06:18.260,0:06:22.420
Ndinotenda Mwari nekukushandisa imi kuti muudze baba vangu

0:06:22.420,0:06:28.560
nokuti pandinenge ndiri kuchikoro, ndinoona vabereki vevamwe vachiuya kwavari kuchikoro.

0:06:28.560,0:06:32.660
Saka, iko zvino ndinofara kuti ndava na baba vangu.

